      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, you said the claims are \"legitimate\" for all of them but earlier you mentioned China's actions are \"widely criticized\" and \"assertive\". if the UNCLOS framework is the standard, doesn't that mean China's claims are actually illegal according to international law? or are you saying they're just another valid opinion?",
